<br>
DS is in 80% of cases our most mana-efficiant spell. FoT can be resisted (even partially) or the Los may not be clear (wasting 500 mana, minus the specialisation &amp; co). The only case i don't DS the MT of the group is when we have 3+ tanks getting hit and the mobs are slowed.<br>
<br>
I also use rokyl channeling staff (the thing of the named FG in solB) to extent the duration of the DS and make it even more mana efficiant.<br>
